data.text:
About Aralaguppe

Aralaguppe is a village in Tiptur tehsil in district of Tumkur, Karnataka, India. As per the data provided by Census of India in 2011, total population of Aralaguppe was 2,247 which includes 1,098 males and 1,149 females. Aralaguppe covers 1115.64 ha area. Pincode of Aralaguppe is 572212.
